article.description: — Jalen Hodge registered 16 points as James Madison narrowly beat Old Dominion 58-53 on Saturday.
article.headline: Hodge carries James Madison over Old Dominion 58-53
article.linkText: Hodge carries James Madison over Old Dominion 58-53
article.story: HARRISONBURG, Va. -- — Jalen Hodge registered 16 points as James Madison narrowly beat Old Dominion 58-53 on Saturday. Vado Morse had 11 points for James Madison (2-0). Charles Falden added 10 points. C.J. Keyser had 21 points for the Monarchs (1-1). Kalu Ezikpe added 11 points. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/hub/college-basketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
